response.overview: The first DVD of a most intriguing prog rock band from Finland! Filmed and recorded at the first edition of Prog Rock Festival at the Wyspianski Theatre in Katowice, Poland, the release features particularly eclectic music played with charisma, technical perfection, and wit. With the scope of their music covering classic rock, ambient soundscapes and even heavy metal elements, Overhead constantly surprise the listener with their great resourcefulness and ability to shift between diverse musical hues and shades.
response.title: Overhead - Live After All
